Rename r8152.c with r8152_main.c. Move some basic definitions from
r8152_main.c to r8152_basic.h. Move the relative code of firmware
from r8152_main.c to r8152_fw.c. Rename the definition of "EFUSE"
with "USB_EFUSE".

